form_title.ms_form_title_llm_v1: Commissioner, Central Office Congressional Mail Unit, CO 703.540

full_text: Commissioner, Central Office January 3, 1974 Congressional Mail Unit Francis P. Murphy, Officer-in Charge, Albany, N. Y. 12201 Your CO 703.540 dated December 20, 1973; Julian J. WU Dr. Julian J. Wu, a naturalized citizen of the United States submitted a visa petition on July 2, 1973 to accord immediate relative status to his mother, Wu, Chi-Su. The petition was approved on January 2, 1974 and the appropriate forms for the beneficiary's adjustment were furnished.
